channel.title: Help Please ! Client issues
channel.description:
Okay, i just recently downloaded TorvapkzV1-3 and i got the source working and im using a webclient right now off a website, and the client that came with this i can't seem to get working, i got it from https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=495620.0
i don't know what to change in client.java or gui.java because there is something like http://127.0.0.1/cache and that threw me off guard because i haven't seen that before.
If someone could teamviewer me or give me detailed instructions on what i have to change so the client matches up with my source, that would be greatly appreciated, thank you!
